法來勢洶洶，在世界新聞自由日，業界對新聞自由評分跌至新低，香港電台開始清洗歷史紀錄、移除正直稱職的記者。<br />\n<br />\n選擇踏上這條路不是草率的決定，無論贏或輸，案件最終或須上移至終審法院，我已有一定的心理準備。身為傳媒人，我一直以報道事實、說真話為志業，在我城崩壞之時，我期許自己「活在真實中」，真誠、善良、正直地活著。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/684887020/posts/10157821915147021/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F684887020%2Fposts%2F10157821915147021%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn822uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=3773b887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/684887020/posts/10157821915147021/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"0471f9e7ea06a96849cec0d6f553393a94f13d77","tid":2517128,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75e7f946e01597d80ab2d6bbf71825722a2353d","tid":2517128,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:36:43.000Z","msg":"今次DOJ會唔會介入？"},{"pid":"7d6a8703f06d56ae72bc5c330e28218ab79b692f","tid":2517128,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:37:47.000Z","msg":"傻嘅先再浪費錢係司法制度入邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔會課金俾任何打官司嘅基金"},{"pid":"ddf886cdc12dc6589214c3d3e246c81496e1e9c3","tid":2517128,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0527a3d4eb8d700fcd3beb2f8d0c4625fda2b857","tid":2517128,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8eaf50f17fe71f7090abbba398f48ceea591c6f","tid":2517128,"uid":345459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 舉腳支持"},{"pid":"77065d